CalculatedMember.formula: SUM(TOPCOUNT([Categories.Default].[三级品类].CurrentMember.Children, 3, [Measures].[品牌销量]),[Measures].[品牌销量] ) / [Measures].[品牌销量]

CalculatedMember.name: CR8
CalculatedMember.formula: SUM(TOPCOUNT([Categories.Default].[三级品类].CurrentMember.Children, 8, [Measures].[品牌销量]),[Measures].[品牌销量] ) / [Measures].[品牌销量]
